        "Pairwise Feature Plots:\n",
        "Create scatterplots for pairs of features. This allows you to visualize the relationship between two features at a time.\n",
        "\n",
        "Parallel Coordinates:\n",
        "Represent each feature as a vertical axis and connect data points with lines. Each line represents an instance in your dataset.\n",
        "This technique allows you to visualize relationships between multiple features simultaneously.\n",
        "\n",
        "Heatmaps:\n",
        "Create heatmaps to visualize correlations between features. Heatmaps can help you identify which features are strongly correlated with each other.\n",
